instructions.original_snippets:
**NEVER wrap HSL values in `hsl()` inside `@theme inline`.**
In Tailwind v4, `--color-primary: hsl(174 90% 31%)` inside `@theme inline` will double-wrap when Tailwind generates utilities, producing broken output.
/* ✅ GOOD */
:root { --primary: hsl(174 90% 31%); }
@theme inline { --color-primary: var(--primary); }

:root {
  --background: hsl(0 0% 100%);
  ...--radius: 0.5rem;
}

@layer base {
  body {
    background-color: var(--background);
    color: var(--foreground);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }
}
